details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Another group coming! Hold the line!

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: City is already under attack, but it looks like they can take care of themselves.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: We should focus on taking out the Ruby Dusk base.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: First of all, we need some production capabilities. Engineers managed to set up a camp, but they were spooked by an enemy Tank and abandoned the site. We just have to claim it.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Ruby Dusk is setting up an artillery unit to hit the city from afar.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Their HQ is located here. It seems they are holding a VIP there as well. I almost expected it would be Commando Blake, but it does not look like it.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: There is another, smaller base as well. We should take it out before we attempt an attack on the HQ, otherwise we might expose our flank.
Establish Base in Sapphire Dawn camp.
Capture the Ruby Dusk HQ.
General Cyrus must survive.
(Optional) Capture the Ruby Dusk forward Camp.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: I have made a tactical mistake! Fall back!

details.name: Messenger
details.text: Our forward base has been taken by Sapphire Dawn!

details.name: Officer
details.text: Send out a call for reinforcements.

details.name: Messenger
details.text: Our forward base has been taken by Sapphire Dawn!

details.name: Officer
details.text: Send out a call for reinforcements.

details.name: Officer
details.text: Sapphire Dawn is really pushing on us. We need a more skilled commander.

details.name: Officer
details.text: Bring in the prisoner!

details.name: Guard
details.text: Are you sure, sir? Lord Dawson might not be happy when he hears about this.

details.name: Officer
details.text: He also won't be happy if we won't stand our ground effectively, since we are not able to retreat...

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: I've heard you summoned me, commander.

details.name: Officer
details.text: Situation is getting difficult, Sir. General Cyrus arrived not long ago, and he is already giving us a lot of trouble.

details.name: Officer
details.text: My troops need someone a lot more experienced to lead them. I am asking you to take command.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: I see. I hate to admit it, but this current predicament might be due to my own making. Even so, I'll do what I can to help.

details.name: Officer
details.text: Thank you, Sir!
(Optional) Defeat Noble Sidney.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Bested by Warlord Grim's lackeys. What a shame to see honourable General Cyrus doing mercenary work.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: What are you even talking about? Bring him in for questioning.
(Done) Defeat Noble Sidney.

details.name: Sergeant
details.text: Objective complete, Sir. Ruby Dusk soldiers are standing down.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Tell me something Sidney. Why has Lord Dawson ordered an attack on Amber Noon lands? How come, that a lust for conquest overcame his senses?

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Pah. What lies. Is that what Warlord Grim told you?

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Enlighten me then.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: It was Amber Noon who attacked us first, whithout any provocation. It was only fair to strike back.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: I might have gotten a bit carried away with that counter-attack, though...

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Hahaha, is that how you ended up behind bars?

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Gloat all you want, but it's not me doing dirty work for that tin-head Warlord.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: These are some serious accusations. I might have to call President Gideon and ask him about that deal he has with Grim...

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Oh, and speaking of tin-heads. Do you know anything about Commando Blake's whereabouts?

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: You don't know where your own man is? That's hilarious. I've heard he got beaten quite badly while trying to assault Rubyport. He seems to have dissapeared afterwards.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: That idiot did WHAT?
